data.description: Motivated Sellers, this Nearly new home is now available, tucked away in a quiet subdivision. Home was built in 2021, Craftsman constructed  with brick on 3 sides. The Cali floorplan boasts 4 bedrooms, 2 full baths, covered deck and patio along with 2 car garage. Home has updated neutral white paint throughout. Open floor plan is conducive to entertaining with access to the covered deck. Kitchen is complete with stainless steel appliances, walk in corner pantry and large island with seating. The EVP flooring is durable throughout the main living areas, with carpet in the bedrooms. Home has a Smart Home Connect system which includes a camera doorbell and keyless entry. Home also has a regularly maintained HVAC system with warrantied Ultraviolet Light system installed. Privacy fence and large yard with separate pavered social area complete the exterior of the home. Home does have an assumable VA loan. Buyer must be VA eligible. Buyer to verify all measurements and other items important to buyer.
